partnerDetails.about:
Central Data Networks Pty Ltd, ICT Solutions

Central Data Networks Pty Ltd [CDN] is an Australian IT solutions provideer, software development company (ISO9001 & ISO13485 accredited) and managed services provider who have been in business for over 25 years. We specialise in Cloud solutions, Healthcare Portals, Business Systems Design & Integration, Project Management Services, Analytics, Radiology Information Systems [RIS], Picture Archive Communication Systems [PACS], Cardiovascular Information Systems [CVIS] and third party integration solutions for Enterprise Healthcare solutions.
